data.description: This setting defines the Y coordinate of the Z-seam when the 'Z seam alignment' is set to 'user specified'.
data.img_description: The left model has the seam on the front, the Y-value is zero. The right model has the seam on the back, the Y-value is 230.
data.hints: - The coordinates are calculated absolute or relative depending on the preference of the user.
